\par }{\f0\fs22\cf1\insrsid4089905\charrsid12391684 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 As we explained earlier, after the Big Bang, particle\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 s emerged and came together as ATOMS. Well, do you know what an atom is? 
